* Proper GNU build system
* The following capabilities should be create parameters
  (from linux/blk_types.h)
        * FLUSH (REQ_FLUSH)
        * FUA (REQ_FUA)
        * DISCARD (REQ_DISCARD)
        * SECURE DISCARD (REQ_DISCARD | REQ_SECURE)

* Do direct IO on tunnel device to speed things up
* Create python binding for quick prototyping
